      <blockquote>
        <P><font face="Arial" size="4" color="#000000">Prayer:&nbsp; </font><font face="Arial" color="#ffffff" size="3">The focus of this team is on praying for the needs of the congregation and requests that have been submitted.  They meet as a group as well of with those seeking soaking prayer.</font></P>

        <P><font face="Arial" size="4" color="#000000">Outreach:&nbsp; </font><font face="Arial" color="#ffffff" size="3">This lively team brainstorms activities that might appeal to those outside the church, aka "Servant Evangelism."  It plans non-threatening events to which we can invite friends. Outreach also helps administer our benevolence focus.</font></P>

        <P><font face="Arial" size="4" color="#000000">Adult Christian
        Education:&nbsp; </font><font face="Arial" color="#ffffff" size="3">Adult CE 
        covers adult Bible classes, small group studies, and 
        discipleship ministries.</font></P>

        <P><font face="Arial" size="4" color="#000000">Youth:&nbsp;</font><font face="Arial" color="#ffffff" size="3">
        This group assists the youth pastor in carrying out ministry among our
        youth.</font></P>

        <P><font face="Arial" size="4" color="#000000">Pastoral:&nbsp; </font><font face="Arial" color="#ffffff" size="3">These
        individuals are on-call to assist the Lead Pastor in counseling and
        deliverance ministries.&nbsp;&nbsp;</font></P>

